• The appellant spoke, read and wrote Indonesian and spoke Hokkian but did not otherwise speak, read or write English; 

• The appellant required an interpreter in the Indonesian language;

• The application was prepared with the assistance of Erwin Marzukie, a registered migration agent, who was the appellant's migration agent.

